 BBNaija’s Nina has stepped on the toes of many after trashing the popular ‘Zazoo’ hit song. Zazoo Zehh is the latest sensational street song by Nigerian singer Portable and has remained on the lips of many music lovers. However, Nina decided to share her two cent stating that people are overhyping the music as she struggled to understand what portable is singing. In her words: I feel like you guys are overhyping this song because I’ve been trying so hard to understand what this guy but it’s not working. What does this song mean exactly coz hmmm. READ ALSO: BBNaija’s Nina Celebrates Her Son As He Clocks One The statement did not sit well with many Nigerians as they dragged her, reminding her how her stay in the Big Brother Naija house was also overhyped. olayinkaoo wrote: It is not overhyped madam Nina… You don’t need to understand a certain language before it makes sense to you what of the beats? I love Flavours song I am not ibo . Pls appreciate talent 